| Executive Orders | KXEO* | Federal Register | $30K-$100K |\\n\\n#### Data Sour
ces for Edge\\n\\n- **Legislative:** Congress.gov API, GovTrack, ProPublica Cong
ress API\\n- **News:** Real-time news feeds with NLP sentiment analysis\\n- **So
cial:** Twitter/X political sentiment, prediction market aggregation\\n- **Exper
t:** Political forecasting models (FiveThirtyEight, Prediction markets consensus
)\\n\\n#### Model Approach\\n\\n```\\nFeatures:\\n- Legislative progress indicat
ors (committee votes, cosponsors)\\n- News sentiment (NLP on political news)\\n-
