--|---------------------|\\n| Economics | 5% | 55-60% | 3-7% of bankroll |\\n| C
rypto | 3% | 53-57% | 2-5% of bankroll |\\n| Politics | 3% | 53-56% | 2-4% of ba
nkroll |\\n\\n### Fee Considerations\\n\\n- Kalshi charges taker fees (higher wh
en odds are uncertain ~50/50)\\n- Maker fees are zero (incentive to provide liqu
idity)\\n- **Strategy:** Use limit orders where possible to avoid taker fees\\n\
