vidence on Prediction Market Efficiency\\n\\nKey findings from GWU research on K
alshi data (2021-2025):\\n\\n1. **Favorite-Longshot Bias:** Prices are systemati
cally biased predictors — favorites win more often than prices imply, longshots 
